sourcesContent: import React from "react"; import { Box, Typography, Tabs, Tab, Grid, Paper } from "@mui/material"; import PieChartOutlineIcon from '@mui/icons-material/PieChartOutline'; function Sales() { return ( Customer Billing Area {/* Tabs */} {/* Sales Actions Grid */} Sales {[ "Create Quick Sales", "Create Detailed Invoice", "Invoices List", "Create Sales Order", "Sales Order List", "Customers invoices", "Create Prospects", "Prospects List", "New Contract", "List of contracts", "Create Contact", "List of contacts /address", "Create Customer", "Customer Details", "Template invoice", "Payments received from customers", "Create Proposal", "Proposals" ].map((label, idx) => ( {label} ))} {/* Settings */} Settings {[ "Product Accounting", "Vat accounts", "Customers tags /categories", "Contacts tags /categories", "Generate Barcode" ].map((text, idx) => ( {text} ))} {/* Statistics Section (Pie Chart Placeholder) */} Statistics - Customer Invoice Draft Starter Paid Closed Total 2 ); } export default Sales;
